{"title":"西藏谚语","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":4,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"·西藏谚语·"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披着虎皮的驴子，谁也吓唬不倒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白纸黑字，神力难移。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要辨明云行的方向，要懂得尘起的原因。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再好的铜和铁，也须千锤百炼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泡沫冒处，必有浅滩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过于逞能，最后是会要哭的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羊头安在马身上——颠倒黑白。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}